name: 2 Fast 4 Gnomz
overview: In 2 Fast 4 Gnomz, join Bumb, Berzerk, Speedster and Uncle Time as they run, fly, bounce, glide and break their way through the magical lands of Gnomia to reach their mysterious destiny. You can help them save the kingdom, find a princess and collect hundreds of precious lost socks. Run faster than a speeding rabbit! Leap large holes in a single bound! Become more powerful than a raging elephant!
